graph TB
    subgraph "Model Registry Operator"
        Controller[model-registry-operator<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Service<br/>Port 9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Managed Model Registry Instance"
        direction TB
        RestAPI[model-registry REST service<br/>Port 8080/TCP HTTP]
        Proxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Port 8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+]
        Database[(PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>Port 5432/3306)]

        Proxy -->|forwards to| RestAPI
        RestAPI -->|persists to| Database
    end

    subgraph "Optional Features"
        Catalog[Model Catalog<br/>Curated metadata]
    end

    User[User/Client] -->|creates| ModelRegistryCR[ModelRegistry CR<br/>v1beta1]
    ModelRegistryCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| RestAPI
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Proxy
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Database
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Services[Services<br/>Routes<br/>NetworkPolicies]

    Controller -->|optional| Catalog

    ExternalDB[(External PostgreSQL<br/>or MySQL)] -.->|alternative| RestAPI

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
    Controller -.->|optional| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS certs]
    Controller -.->|optional| ServiceMesh[Istio/Service Mesh<br/>VirtualService]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Controller -->|watches| PlatformComponents[components.platform.opendatahub.io]
    Controller -->|watches| PlatformServices[services.platform.opendatahub.io<br/>auths]

    %% External Access
    ExternalClient[External Client] -->|HTTPS 443| Route[OpenShift Route]
    Route -->|forwards to| Proxy

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style RestAPI fill:#4a90e2
    style Proxy fill:#7ed321
    style ModelRegistryCR fill:#f5a623
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8
    style ServiceMesh fill:#e8e8e8
    style PlatformComponents fill:#7ed321
    style PlatformServices fill:#7ed321
    style Database fill:#d0d0d0
    style ExternalDB fill:#d0d0d0
